<template>
  <section>
    <SongList :songs="songs" />
  </section>
</template>

<script>
import SongList from "../components/SongList.vue";

export default {
  name: "App",
  components: {
    SongList
  },
  methods: {
    async fetchSongs() {
      const res = await fetch("http://localhost:5000/songs");
      const data = await res.json();

      return data;
    }
  },
  data() {
    return {
      songs: Object
    };
  },
  async created() {
    this.songs = await this.fetchSongs();
  }
};
</script>

<style lang="scss">
@import "../shared/_styles.scss";

section {
  background-color: $main-gray;
  padding: 1vw;
}
</style>
